{"tid":2352840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子被控禮賓府外隧道意圖用噴漆塗鴉　判監14天緩刑2年","createTime":"2021-01-04T09:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T13:20:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"16f604a512deaccb572d610b3d66adb6b9d6d46b","tid":2352840,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12601&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=dfc1b0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12601</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第十庭 <br />\n#黃雅茵裁判官 #判刑<br />\n#0915中環 <br />\n#管有物品意圖損壞財產罪<br />\n<br />\n王(33)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有物品意圖損壞財產<br />\n<br />\n簡單判刑理由：<br />\n被告被控於2019年9月15日，在中環花園道與上亞厘畢道交界行人隧道近燈柱號碼24273，保管2樽噴漆，意圖在無合理辯解的情況下，用以損壞公眾地方行人隧道的牆壁。面向牆壁，搖動，未來得及噴，被拘捕，曾表示&ldquo;SORRY SIR 有悔意&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n由於被告不想與感化官談論此案，以及不透露任何個人資料。只能依賴法庭上提供資料，33歲獨居，中大碩士博士在讀生。沒有任何求情資料提供。本案前沒有刑事定罪紀錄。事發地點與示威地點不接近，沒有證據顯示被告想在牆上噴什麼，不應把本案將於示威相關的案件相提並論。<br />\n<br />\n🛑14天監禁，緩刑兩年🛑<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n庭上被告曾做出自辯，質疑控罪：<br />\n控方觀點混淆，民事刑事訴訟混淆，應該是民事罪行，屬於行為不檢。但你判刑是刑事罪行，希望你看看香港法律的民事和刑事分別，管有財產企圖破壞罪應該是極權北韓法庭才能判的，如果我科學來講沒有做出任何破壞行為。並沒有在牆壁做出任何有科學根據的破壞行為，企圖破壞是一個思想，為何刑事罪成立？應該民事訴訟檢控行為不檢，3位警員有配槍，當事人只是想行去山頂鋸扒。管有財產罪意圖破壞是意識形態上，北韓極權國家才應有的罪。我當時沒有做出任何破壞。我原意想去山頂鋸扒，右手手握著認為可飲用的噴漆。3名證人曾噴過該噴漆，造成不公，他們誹謗當事人合法上山頂凌霄閣鋸扒的權利。"},{"pid":"d3e7e59314744f891c5a86b6285d275a7dac88ba","tid":2352840,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"在控罪書報稱學生的被告，過往無案底，他自稱畢業於中大中醫學系，又宣稱自己正研讀中大法律系碩士課程，及自修法律博士課程。他被控於2019年9月15日，在中環花園道與上亞厘畢道交界行人隧道保管有2樽噴漆，意圖在無合理辯解的情況下，用以損壞行人隧道的牆壁。<br />\n<br />\n被告沒有律師代表，他今日親自求情時，批評法庭混淆法律觀點，說路政署本應民事檢控他行為不檢，但警方卻刑事起訴他；他又說管有物品意圖摧毀財產的控罪「响北韓呢類極權國家先會有」，更表示當日原本是「上山鋸扒」，而噴漆是拿來喝的，希望法庭考慮憐憫他予以輕判。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官黃雅茵表示，被告被定罪後拒絕回答感化官的問題及披露自己的背景，法庭只能依賴他向法庭提供的資料判刑。而案中並無證據證明與示威相關，故以監禁14天為量刑起點，雖然並無減刑因素，但可以緩刑處理。"},{"pid":"c75e15c9527bc82950d9750ce33fa72982389f1d","tid":2352840,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3752ef71ca97bc5307a37a011354740f1d661a98","tid":2352840,"uid":327169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"黑警每人有支槍，算唔算管有物品意圖傷害他人???<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804328df2b5d2a5402c2c75398c1999f7d14909a","tid":2352840,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"有鳩=意圖強姦"},{"pid":"3fabdd0d4292fc1ae9eda5e361a2ead9b77e6069","tid":2352840,"uid":134323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"而案中並無證據證明與示威相關，故以監禁14天為量刑起點，雖然並無減刑因素，但可以緩刑處理。<br />\n<br />\n示威相關係加刑原因，戲都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934e4208b780f04e194427d74b97b210444bd6b6","tid":2352840,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">損壞財產</span><br />\n唔講仲以為用噴漆炸左條隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52159bf2092f9f6a59b903e902e7bb281d878e87","tid":2352840,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fabdd0d4292fc1ae9eda5e361a2ead9b77e6069","tid":2352840,"uid":134323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"而案中並無證據證明與示威相關，故以監禁14天為量刑起點，雖然並無減刑因素，但可以緩刑處理。<br />\n<br />\n示威相關係加刑原因，戲都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"梗係啦，唔關示威事，波台狗就覺得係鬼嚟"},{"pid":"14c2d6ad5815ca71b7061e9967e10c834bf47061","tid":2352840,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"現場無噴過就亂砌"},{"pid":"3e040a7f27db8a4f63a23685bf9b64ab53598e3b","tid":2352840,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"其實佢如果有請律師應該有機會打得甩?"},{"pid":"131302c268e25152e9668f0d76a9510f2406023c","tid":2352840,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d10ca5da842b7af7167c5d40eba482cd9a383fc","tid":2352840,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"公眾地方行為不檢都係刑事嚟㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ac91a008d560544ee5d306cca882df1c88f7d1","tid":2352840,"uid":172172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3fabdd0d4292fc1ae9eda5e361a2ead9b77e6069","tid":2352840,"uid":134323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"而案中並無證據證明與示威相關，故以監禁14天為量刑起點，雖然並無減刑因素，但可以緩刑處理。<br />\n<br />\n示威相關係加刑原因，戲都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:18:48.000Z","msg":"唔係示威就炸左條隧道都得<br />\n係示威就粉筆寫字都要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a21138497474676406dfad4e159783e698b7c46","tid":2352840,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"2019 年 9 月 15 日有網民發起港島遊行，一名 33 歲男子涉於當日管有兩樽噴漆，經審訊後被裁定管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪成。被告自稱中大法律系「博士自修生」，今（4 日）在西九龍裁判法院求情時，批評這條控罪「只有喺北韓極權先會發生」，屬於「意識形態」的罪行，要求裁判官「好心好心你睇吓條控罪」、「提高慈愛、仁愛之心」。他最終被判囚 14 天，緩刑 2 年。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85%E6%89%B9%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA-%E5%8F%AA%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F-%E5%AE%98%E5%88%A4%E7%B7%A9%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=e99b857d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25BC%2586%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=9ab3f3ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E8%97%8F%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85%E6%89%B9%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA-%E5%8F%AA%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F-%E5%AE%98%E5%88%A4%E7%B7%A9%E5%88%91/</a>"},{"pid":"f7d10c9f305a0e25668390ec339b06df166f745e","tid":2352840,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"被告又要求裁判官「好心反省下點解判我有罪」。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/ITUWX6JSWZAZXDCDA32AQHK2S4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210104%2FITUWX6JSWZAZXDCDA32AQHK2S4%2F&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=2ecbab0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210104%2FITUWX6JSWZAZXDCDA32AQHK2S4%2F&h=f654004e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/ITUWX6JSWZAZXDCDA32AQHK2S4/</a>"},{"pid":"9107b36771719fde48afad2194eb021898f3851b","tid":2352840,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5edb7b6d71a764339179f595c14c246b5a1db4b","tid":2352840,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}